# Optional — Query Hub API runs on another host (e.g. dba-kiro). Vite dev server proxies /api here.
# Example after: tsh ssh -L 3003:127.0.0.1:3003 …   → keep http://localhost:3003
# Or point to a tunneled / internal URL:
# VITE_DEV_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:3003

# Optional — “Connect to Kiro host (Teleport)” button in Kiro → Connection (Kiro CLI mode)
# Paste your Teleport web UI link to the dba-kiro (SSH) resource or pinned resource view.
# VITE_TELEPORT_KIRO_HOST_URL=https://your-teleport.example.com/web/...
